-- Paulson to Vote All Shares in Favor of Freeport’s Plains Offer
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2013-05-20T14:10:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-20/paulson-to-vote-all-shares-in-favor-of-freeport-s-plains-offer.html
 Paulson & Co. said it supports
 Freeport-McMoRan Copper & Gold Inc. (FCX) ’s $6.12 billion takeover bid
for Plains Exploration & Production Co. after the terms of the
deal were sweetened.  Paulson will vote its 12.8 million Plains shares,
representing a stake of about 9.9 percent, in favor of the deal,
the hedge-fund firm said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
